title: 10: Wall Street Wants Your Data (Rebroadcast)
description:
The Readback team is taking a quick break. We'll be back with a new episode next week. In the meantime, we've selected one of our favorite episodes to re-release. In this episode, we look closer at the booming world of alternative data-and how investors can make use of it. Originally broadcast on December 5, 2018.
